[16/04/2019 06:17:43] <font color="#ffffff">ser... ser...</font>
[16/04/2019 06:17:47] <font color="#ffffff">homosexual o fetichista,</font>
[16/04/2019 06:17:47] <font color="#ffffff">lésbico o sádico...</font>
