[16/04/2019 13:30:21] <font color="#ffffff">¡Vamos!</font>
[16/04/2019 13:30:29] <font color="#ffffff">¡Ea! ¡Ea!</font>
[16/04/2019 13:30:34] <font color="#ffffff">¡Vamos, vamos!</font>
[16/04/2019 13:30:37] <font color="#ffffff">¡Bill, Enny, vamos!</font>
